{"id":"5364","user":{"id":"214296","nickname":"主播喵副本","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FmnbCWV2OzmsQSOnJc8r6Tte5W25","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【mod】萌新院第二课","content":"<p>你是否还在为不知道怎么更改东西的名字而烦恼呢？不用烦恼，mod来帮你！（虽然说我的世界里也有这种功能）</p>\n<p>下面就是模块喵了！</p>\n<p>喵！蓝翔搬运！</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FleYY0uC9n02ipH8JFJUqR6wJGCr\"><br></p>\n<p>我们决定先让李狗蛋来作死一下。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FkVqasYxqFr8w9GGEC9HJlq3M75k\"><br></p>\n<p>呃呃呃···这个是虾米鬼！设置成立名称为不成立···</p>\n<p>成立是叫true，而不成立叫false</p>\n<p>把成立更改为不成立，这到底是什么逻辑。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>好了，接下来正经点。这个模块呢，主要有这几种用法。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FlT37iju81kiuIKbirZUgNe91LKd\"><br></p>\n<p>改变世界名称</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FpI8MCJBKHM91fbd0SfnonC444Vd\"><br></p>\n<p>改变物品名称</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FqXVF4KHyC-JERc9_ro9crIRZH5z\"><br></p>\n<p>设置玩家名称。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fqi-1aVdF3oHUoFhI1lMNL4A2_cB\"><br></p>\n<p>设置焦点实体名称。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FsCEXuYlHx7vOPyO-_JD_UTZTxDI\"><br></p>\n<p>设置玩家物品栏第X栏名称。</p>\n<p>以及好多好多你想不到的用处。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font size=\"5\" color=\"#ff0000\">今天的mod教学课程就到这里啦，更多精彩请关注萌新院，QQ群号：586884452</font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></p>","board_id":"2","board_name":"积木编程乐园","updated_at":1502070703,"created_at":1501990409,"n_views":200,"n_replies":9,"n_comments":1,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":false,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}